title: Hunter Symphony
description: With graceful, sweeping blades, elegant lines and a glossy white finish, the Symphony is a soft modern masterpiece. It’s also Wi-Fi enabled and boasts support for Apple HomeKit technology, allowing you to control the fan from anywhere and seamlessly connect it with other HomeKit-enabled products. Debuted at the 2016 Consumer Electronics Show in Las Vegas, the Symphony – and our other Wi-Fi enabled, HomeKit-enabled fan, Signal – allow you to effortlessly step into the world of home automation.
